Idea of the program:

1. user runs the program 

2. program shows 6 options:
		1. Show ToDo's
		2. add item
		3. remove item
		4. change item
		5. Mark as DONE
		
2.1 Shows ToDo List
2.2 Adds an item to the end of ToDo List
2.3 Removes an item at index i from the ToDoList
2.4 Changes an item at index i of ToDoList to the new Item 'item'
2.5 Marks an item as DONE and moves it to the top of The List
